{
  "stem": "11797.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And finally, the train was going back and forth, back and forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In that train, they had people from the whole world, that train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I told you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it was going back and forth continuously.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Nobody said a word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Everybody was quiet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Supposedly, I heard after the war that they were going to take us back to Dachau to be killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Then somebody said that the last train, the last car had gasoline.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They were going to blow us up, which was true.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They were going to blow us up, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Fortunately, there was a Frenchman that released the opening from that barrel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He let all the gas out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Somebody told him that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And the train went in partially to a tunnel, partially and stayed there because the airplanes were going and throwing bombs and everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We saw a little bit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We saw a light.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "My car was a little bit of light showing down, and the rest were in tunnel or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I didn't know exactly-- I thought, like I mentioned before, to me it didn't matter anymore what it was going to be.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And kept very quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It got very quiet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we sat there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "The Germans went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "My car, the car was in, half way in a tunnel, there was half exposed of light, and we were maybe 3/4 length in the tunnel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I know it was very dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I remember that today.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And somebody opened up the produce car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I heard they opened up, and they threw bread, the haftlinge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "The prisoners themselves opened up supply car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They threw the bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "They threw the margarine.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
